      <title>以色列央行行长预计经济增长将回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-21/bank-of-israel-governor-expects-growth-to-pick-up-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列银行行长阿米尔·亚隆谈到了加沙战争对经济的影响。他预计，如果敌对行动结束，经济增长将会加快。他在瑞士达沃斯举行的世界经济论坛年会上接受彭博电视台丽莎·阿布拉莫维奇的采访。
（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-21/bank-of-israel-governor-expects-growth-to-pick-up-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 16:01:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>应法国要求，欧盟将削减 ESG 报告规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/eu-is-set-to-cut-back-esg-reporting-rules-amid-french-demands-m66nq83f</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法国准备公布旨在限制监管框架范围的正式提案之际，欧盟可能会缩减其备受争议的 ESG 报告要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/eu-is-set-to-cut-back-esg-reporting-rules-amid-french-demands-m66nq83f</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:38:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普暗示即将加征关税，加元接近新冠疫情时期低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/loonie-nears-covid-era-low-as-trump-signals-looming-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示将很快对美国邻国征收关税，随后加元跌至近五年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/loonie-nears-covid-era-low-as-trump-signals-looming-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:31:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多称特朗普的关税措施旨在制造混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-s-tariff-whiplash-is-designed-to-sow-chaos-trudeau-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普正试图在其贸易伙伴中制造不确定性，以使他们失去平衡并削弱他们在贸易谈判中的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-s-tariff-whiplash-is-designed-to-sow-chaos-trudeau-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:30:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Prosus 首席执行官谈人工智能投资如何推动增长市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-21/prosus-ceo-ai-investments-to-supercharge-growth-markets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Prosus 和 Naspers 集团首席执行官 Fabricio Bloisi 与彭博社的 Brenda Tsai 在达沃斯彭博大厦共同探讨人工智能如何调整商业模式、创造公平竞争环境，以及改变增长型市场如何为全球数字经济做出贡献并蓬勃发展的本质。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-21/prosus-ceo-ai-investments-to-supercharge-growth-markets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:28:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顶级航运公司 MSC 暂时将继续避开红海</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/shipping-giant-msc-says-it-will-keep-avoiding-red-sea-for-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[集装箱班轮公司地中海航运有限公司 (MSC Mediterranean Shipping Co. SA) 表示，它将继续派遣其船只绕行非洲南端，直至另行通知，这表明红海的正常贸易流通不会很快恢复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/shipping-giant-msc-says-it-will-keep-avoiding-red-sea-for-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 14:28:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉信理财盈利超出预期，资金流入创纪录，股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/schwab-rises-after-earnings-top-estimates-on-record-inflows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉信理财公司 (Charles Schwab Corp.) 公布的业绩超出华尔街预期，其零售经纪业务继续吸引创纪录的资金流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/schwab-rises-after-earnings-top-estimates-on-record-inflows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 12:44:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪称保险公司将深化私人信贷联系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/insurers-expected-to-deepen-ties-to-private-credit-moody-s-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级报告称，私人信贷和保险公司之间的联系预计今年将更加密切，这可能促使监管机构检查两者之间的关系及任何相关风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/insurers-expected-to-deepen-ties-to-private-credit-moody-s-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普继续威胁征收关税，大宗商品价格回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对墨西哥和加拿大发出关税威胁，再次引发贸易战担忧，石油和工业金属价格下跌，而黄金价格则因投资者寻求避险资产而上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-21</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 23:33:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员期待特朗普提振，华尔街上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市与美元和债券一起上涨，交易员关注唐纳德·特朗普总统的政策将如何提振世界最大经济体的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 22:26:35 GMT</pubDate>
